[+] Fetching GitHub intelligence...
[+] Scanning public records via Google...
[*] Attempting Google search for "Linus Torvalds"...
[+] Compiling intelligence report...
[*] Report successfully generated: Linus_Torvalds_exposed.pdf
[*] Operation complete.
```

